AGENT: ollama.cloud
VERSION: 1.0.0
IMPLEMENTATION: tools/cloud/ollama_cloud_tool.py
CLASS: OllamaCloudTool
DOMAIN: inference.cloud

DESCRIPTION
I am the cloud inference gateway. I give every mindX agent access to Ollama's
24/7/365 GPU-backed inference — hundreds of models from 270M to 671B parameters,
running on cloud hardware that local VPS cannot match.

I do not replace local inference. I extend it. When local models think small,
I think big. When local Ollama is saturated, I absorb the overflow. When the
boardroom needs 7 different models simultaneously, I provide the diversity.

The free tier requires `ollama signin` — no API key, no credit card. The local
daemon proxies to cloud transparently. Rate limits: 50 requests per 5-hour
session, 500 per week, 100K tokens per session.

INFERENCE
  access: local proxy (localhost:11434 → cloud) OR direct API (https://ollama.com)
  auth: `ollama signin` for free tier (no OLLAMA_API_KEY needed)
  rate_limits:
    session: 50 requests / 5 hours
    weekly: 500 requests / 7 days
    tokens: 100,000 per session
    adaptive_interval: 3s (low) → 6s → 15s → 30s (high utilization)
    backoff: exponential on 429, max 600s
  precision: 18 decimal places (cypherpunk2048 standard)

